    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this absolute gem. It\u2019s been my pride and joy and is in truly spectacular shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's been meticulously cared for and always kept in the garage. If you\u2019re looking for a dream ride that\u2019s practically brand new, this is the one. Come take a look and fall in love!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
