      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. Mechanically flawless, the VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, and the rod bearings were replaced as preventative maintenance. The rear subframe has been reinforced with Turner plates to ensure structural rigidity. Zero oxidation on the undercarriage, original Laguna Seca Blue finish with factory-spec depth, and an interior devoid of bolster wear. Equipped with the variable M differential lock and a perfectly balanced 50/50 weight distribution, this chassis remains the benchmark for analog driver engagement.",
